dio" id="no_sib" name="siblings" value="no">  	<label for="no_sib">no</label><br>	</p>	<div id="birthorder" style="display:none">	<p>What is your birth order? 	<select name="birth_order">		<option value="" selected="selected">choose</option>		<option value="oldest_sib">oldest</option>		<option value="youngest_sib">youngest</option>		<option value="middle_sib">in the middle</option>		</select></p></div>	<p>4. When did you begin using English in your daily life?<br>	<select required name="English">	  <option value="" selected ="selected">choose</option>	  <option value="native">I grew up speaking English as soon as I started to talk.</option>	  <option value="early">I started using English in my earliest days at school.</option>	  <option value="late">I started using English when I was in my teens.</option>	  <option value="adult">I started using English as an adult.</option>	  </select> </p>		  	<p>5. What other languages can you use to converse with other people?  <br>	      <input TYPE="text" NAME="other_lgs" required maxlength="60" size="30"><br>	      <i>If more than one, list them in the order of your comfort or proficiency from most to least.</i>	</p><p>6. What type of job do you have? <br><i>Students: what are you aiming for? Retired: what did you do?</i><br>   <select required NAME="occupation">      <option value="">choose</option>      <option VALUE="arch_eng">Architecture and Engineering</option>      <option VALUE="arts">Arts and Design</option>      <option VALUE="cleaning">Building and Grounds Cleaning</option>      <option VALUE="business">Business and Financial</option>      <option VALUE="service">Community and Social Service</option>      <option VALUE="IT">Computer and Information Technology</option>      <option VALUE="constr">Construction and Extraction</option>      <option VALUE="educ">Education, Training, and Library</option>      <option VALUE="farm">Farming, Fishing, and Forestry</option>      <option